    "One day they accidentally find a secret Evelyn's diary, which tells the story of true love between her and James, people from two different worlds, that can't be together due to class division and social expectations.",
    "However, Evelyn and James finally meet each other at the present day with the help of Emma and Max.",
    "It makes a deeper connection between two plot lines.",
    "4 Fantasy \"The Chronicles of Aetheria\" Fantasy novel with the elements of adventure that tells us the story of a fictional world, Aetheria.",
    "The country is made up of regions corresponding to the five elements: fire, water, air, earth and spirit."
